    <head><lb ed="X" n="0519a17"/>　　　　<persName key="A021578">石塔長老</persName>傳</head>
    <p><anchor n="X.77.1524.0519a18"/><lb ed="X" n="0519a18"/><persName key="A021578">石塔戒</persName>長老。住揚州<placeName key="PL000000010769">石塔院</placeName>。<persName key="A003555">東坡</persName>赴<placeName key="PL000000020967">登州</placeName>。師往迎之。
        <lb ed="X" n="0519a19"/>坡曰。吾欲一見<placeName key="PL000000010769">石塔</placeName>。以行速不及也。師起立曰。只這
        <lb ed="X" n="0519a20"/>是甎浮圖耶。<persName key="A003555">坡</persName>曰。有縫奈何。師曰。若無縫。爭解容得
        <lb ed="X" n="0519a21"/>法界螻蟻。及<persName key="A003555">坡</persName>鎮<placeName key="PL000000010785">維揚</placeName>。師遣侍者投<placeName key="unknown">牒解院</placeName>。<persName key="A003555">坡</persName>問。長
        <lb ed="X" n="0519a22"/>老欲何往。以歸<placeName key="PL000000011593">西湖</placeName>舊隱為對。<persName key="A003555">坡</persName>與僚佐同至<placeName key="PL000000010769">石塔</placeName>。
        <lb ed="X" n="0519a23"/>擊鼓集眾。袖中出疏。使<persName key="A008918">晁無咎</persName>讀之。其詞曰。<persName key="A021578">戒</persName>公長
        <lb ed="X" n="0519a24"/>老。開不二門。施無盡藏。念<placeName key="PL000000011593">西湖</placeName>之久別。亦是偶然。為
        <lb ed="X" n="0519b01"/><persName key="A003555">東坡</persName>而少留。無不可者。一時稽首。重聽白椎。渡口船
        <lb ed="X" n="0519b02"/>回。依舊雲山之色。秋來雨過。一新鐘鼓之音。其為時
        <lb ed="X" n="0519b03"/>賢注戀如此。長老。必為時名德。惜不得詳其始末耳。</p>
